      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"16. WHITE MAGIC did a great job to score by 1.75 lengths over this course and distance last start in a far better run. Needs to be at his best to beat this field but he is up to the challenge. 14. MARUYO JORDAN is in great form, lifting strongly to score last start over 1200m at this track to make it two on the bounce. Haruto Nakayama has been the pilot at his last two wins. Sure to play a big role. 3. KITASAN YUJA lines up for the first time since July 17. Started the last campaign impressively when in the placings over 1400m at this track. Makes plenty of appeal. 8. SPLENDENTE comes here off a break of six-and-a-half months. Worth noting she filled a minor placing when returning from a spell last time in work over 1200m at this track. Worth plenty of thought.\",\"runners\":[16,14,3,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
